---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About Luna Jerney | Antigua Real Estate Development" description="Meet Luna Jerney, your expat real estate agent in Antigua Guatemala. Originally from the Netherlands, helping expats relocate since 2021.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">About</div>
      <h1 class="page-hero__title">Meet Luna Jerney</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__subtitle">Your trusted real estate agent in Antigua Guatemala.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:48px;align-items:start;max-width:960px;margin:0 auto;">
        <div style="border-radius:24px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);max-width:400px;">
          <img src="/images/luna-jerney-placeholder.svg" alt="Luna Jerney" style="width:100%;object-fit:cover;">
        </div>
        <div class="prose">
          <h2>From the Netherlands to Antigua Guatemala</h2>
          <p>Over 5 years ago, I made the life-changing decision to move from the Netherlands to Antigua Guatemala. What started as a dream became a reality — and I've never looked back.</p>
          <p>I fell in love with this city: the stunning colonial architecture, the three majestic volcanoes, the vibrant community, and the incredible quality of life that Antigua offers at a fraction of European costs.</p>
          <h2>Why I Specialize in Helping Expats</h2>
          <p>As a fellow expat, I understand the challenges of buying property in a foreign country. The language barrier, the different legal system, the cultural differences — I've been through it all.</p>
          <p>That's why I specialize in helping expats and Guatemalans abroad navigate the real estate market with confidence. I speak your language — literally and figuratively.</p>
          <h2>Languages I Speak</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>English</strong> — Native-level fluency</li>
            <li><strong>Español</strong> — Fluent, business and legal contexts</li>
            <li><strong>Nederlands</strong> — Native speaker</li>
          </ul>
          <h2>What I Offer</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Deep knowledge of Antigua's neighborhoods and property values</li>
            <li>Connections with trusted lawyers, notaries, and contractors</li>
            <li>Honest, no-pressure guidance — I treat every client like family</li>
            <li>Full support from property search to closing and beyond</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>